<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.6.10">
<l>āmaruvi niraimēytta vaṇiyaraṅkat tammāṉai</l>
<l>kāmarucīrk kalikaṉṟi yoliceyta malipukaḻcēr</l>
<l>nāmaruvu tamiḻmālai nāliraṇṭō ṭiraṇṭiṉaiyum</l>
<l>tāmaruvi vallārmēl cārātī viṉaitāmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>On those who, joining together, master</l>
<l rend="indent">these four-[times]-two-plus two [verses],</l>
<l>The garland in Tamil which the tongue enjoys [and] is full of much glory,</l>
<l>Composed by Kalikaṉṟi of desired esteem about the lord of lovely Araṅkam,</l>
<l>Who, cherishing the cows, grazed the herd, evil fate will never adhere.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
